#   https://wask.fr/les-etoiles-wask-2026-jour-par-jour/
#   https://outnow.ch/Thema/Cannes-2026/
#   http://www.filmneweurope.com/images/FNE%20Critics/cannes2026critics.pdf
#   https://www.cahiersducinema.com/fr-fr/festivals/festival-de-cannes-2026
#     https://www.cahiersducinema.com/festivals/cannes-film-par-film
